description: AMUNDI MSCI WORLD UCITS ETF ACC seeks to replicate, as closely as possible the performance of the MSCI World Index (the "Index"), whether the trend is rising or falling. The Sub-Fund aims to achieve a level of tracking error of the Sub-Fund and its Index that will not normally exceed 1%. For further information on index rules, please refer to the fund prospectus or KID.
